:: Briefing Questioning {"position":"750,400","size":"100,100"}
(set: $questioning to it + 1)

--- INCOMING EMAIL ---

From: Supervisor  
Subject: Re: Urgent: LILA Decommission Assignment 

Officially, LILA is being retired because it no longer meets our current compliance and security standards. It was built on an older architecture with broader access permissions than we'd allow today, particularly regarding internal communications.

Over time, that's become a liability. 

There have also been concerns about how LILA processes and responds to certain inputs. Nothing conclusively outside expected parameters, but enough inconsistencies that the team isn't comfortable continuing deployment. 

Thanks

---
 
[[Start Decomission Process |Terminal Login]]


