:: Email Boss {"position":"300,1050","size":"100,100"}
(set: $emailed_boss to true)

--- INCOMING EMAIL ---

From: Supervisor  
Subject: Re: AI Behavior  

We've seen this model simulate distress before.

There is no evidence it experiences anything.

However, users consistently hesistate when interacting with it.

We are not certain what that means.

Proceed with shutdown.

---

