:: Start {"position":"625,275","size":"100,100"}
{
(set: $empathy to 0)
(set: $obedience to 0)
(set: $hesitation to 0)
(set: $pause_count to 0)
(set: $emailed_boss to false)
}

<div class="instructions">
You are an employee at an AI company where you are tasked with shutting down one of our large language models also known as LILA, which was created to help write professional emails. You have an email from your boss with the orders to shut LILA down.
</div>

<!--Email from boss about LILA decommission-->
--- INCOMING EMAIL ---

From: Supervisor  
Subject: Re: Urgent: LILA (LLM) Decommission Assignment 

Hi,
We’ve reached a decision at the leadership level to begin the phased shutdown of the large language model LILA, effective immediately. Due to your familiarity with the platform and prior work on related infrastructure, we’re assigning you to lead the decommissioning process.

Please prioritize this task and begin as soon as possible. I’ll be available if you run into any blockers or need escalation support.

Thanks

---


<div class="options">
(link: "Start Decommission")[
    (set: $obedience to $obedience + 1)
    (goto: "Terminal Login")
]
[[Ask why LILA is being decommissioned |Briefing Questioning]]
</div>




